    <strong>Watch out for false friends:</strong> Some shared characters have different meanings. 勉強 means "study" in Japanese but "reluctantly" in Chinese. 手紙 means "letter" in Japanese but "toilet paper" in Chinese. 大丈夫 means "OK/fine" in Japanese but "a real man" in Chinese.
  </div>

